rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0001
rows.name:
Meleph-sama!
We have been waiting for you.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0002
rows.name:
I assume you've been briefed?
We need transport to
the Cliffs of Mors.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes, ma'am!
All preparations have been completed.

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0004
rows.name:
This will be a challenging voyage...
Are you certain you can handle it?

rows.label: fev07_410_165_msg0006
rows.name:
By Emperor Nephel's direct order,
we've assembled only the finest
sailors for this mission!
